         As you walk into the ladies, a woman frowns at you. "Not so fast, buddy," she says. "There's a separate facility for your kind." She grabs you by the arm and rudely propels you out of the door. Clearly, that was not the unisex toilet.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Woman walks into gents'>
         It's the smell that first cues you that maybe you've walked through the wrong door. This is confirmed by the man who is standing at the... and he's... oh, there's no need to go into the details! You avert your gaze and back out quickly.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Neuter walks into gents'>
         A chap looks at you very suspiciously as you walk into what is obviously the gents' toilet. You sigh at these oh-so-touchy Earthmen and their preoccupation with gender, but decide you'd better find the unixex toilet.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Man walks into unixex loo'>
