         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='Woman walks into unisex loo'>
         There is a green-skinned being that seems to be drying its tentacles under a hot-air blower, and that makes you realise this is not the toilet for you. You leave fast, before you catch a glimse of alien body parts best left to the imagination.
         </para>

