         <para number='1' comment='Buy food - Starship Cant - 454'>
         You press a button to order some food. With a flash of light, an ice cream sundae materializes on the table in front of you: mounds of creamy vanilla ice cream smothered with a neon pink strawberry sauce, topped with whipped cream and bourbon-flavored almonds. It's delicious, and before long the glass dish is completely empty.
