         </para>

      </section>

      <section name='member'>

         <para number='1' comment='Buy food - members lounge 1037'>
         The waitdroid places a crystal bowl containing tender morsels of flaked tuna in front of you, together with a silver dish of rich cream sauce and some slices of toast. Since nobody much cares about table manners in the lounge, you chomp through the food while continuing to talk to your fellows.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Not enough groats'>
         The waitdroid reminds you that although this is a members club, you still have to pay for food, and that you don't seem to have two groats to rub together right now.
         </para>

      </section>

      <section name='orran'>

         <para number='1' comment='Buy food - Orran s - 1602'>
         You order up a haunch of meat from the animal that is slowly being seared in the pit. It may even be ox, who knows, but whatever the meat's provenance, it's substantial and tasty, even the burnt bits. When you're done, you throw the bones over your shoulder, where they will remain until a cleaning droid gets around to dealing with them.
         </para>

