         <para number='7' comment='christmas/xmas'>
         "This is my busiest time of the year, of course," Santa confides. "I have the elves to help me but I need to supervise them closely, so I don't get any rest at all. Not only do we have to make all the toys, we have to compile the lists, and then spend time in the grotto meeting the children, and finally the big night itself - delivery time!"
